bnf: yarn.resourcemanager.ha.rm-ids in {{rm1,rm2,...}} => yarn.resourcemanager.webapp.address.[rmId] != null for each rmId in yarn.resourcemanager.ha.rm-ids
yarn.nodemanager.resource.count-logical-processors-as-cores = true => yarn.nodemanager.resource.cpu-vcores = number of logical CPUs * yarn.nodemanager.resource.pcores-vcores-multiplier
yarn.resourcemanager.ha.rm-ids in {rm1, rm2} => yarn.resourcemanager.webapp.address = rm1.resourcemanager.webapp.address | rm2.resourcemanager.webapp.address
